name: AVKitError.Code
desc: Constants that identify framework error codes.

items.name: case contentRatingUnknown
items.desc: The media content rating is missing or unrecognized.

items.name: case contentDisallowedByPasscode
items.desc: A restriction disallows access to this content, but the user can override the restriction by entering the device passcode.

items.name: case pictureInPictureStartFailed
items.desc: The system failed to start Picture in Picture.

items.name: case contentDisallowedByProfile
items.desc: An installed profile restricts access to this content.
